{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 18,
  "title": "第十八章（俗薄）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "大道廢，有仁義。"
    },
    {
      "text": "智慧出，有大偽。"
    },
    {
      "text": "六親不和，有孝慈。"
    },
    {
      "text": "國家昏亂，有忠臣。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大道之時，家有孝子，戶有忠信，仁義不見也。大道廢不用，惡逆生，乃有仁義可傳道。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "智慧之君賤德而貴言，賤質而貴文，下則應之以為大偽姦詐。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "六紀絕，親戚不合，乃有孝慈相牧養也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "政令不明，上下相怨，邪僻爭權，乃有忠臣匡正其君也。此言天下太平不知仁，人盡無欲不知廉，各自潔己不知貞。大道之世，仁義沒，孝慈滅，猶日中盛明，眾星失光。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
